  "text": "Identified all RBAC authorization implementation files in kubernetes/kubernetes v1.32.0:\n\n1. **RBACAuthorizer + Authorize method**: `plugin/pkg/auth/authorizer/rbac/rbac.go` \u2014 `RBACAuthorizer` struct with `Authorize()` that uses an `authorizingVisitor` to short-circuit on the first matching `PolicyRule` via `VisitRulesFor`.\n\n2. **SubjectAccessEvaluator**: `plugin/pkg/auth/authorizer/rbac/subject_locator.go` \u2014 `SubjectAccessEvaluator` struct with `AllowedSubjects()` that determines which subjects can perform a given action by checking ClusterRoleBindings and RoleBindings.\n\n3. **DefaultRuleResolver**: `pkg/registry/rbac/validation/rule.go` \u2014 `DefaultRuleResolver` struct implementing `AuthorizationRuleResolver` with `RulesFor()`, `VisitRulesFor()`, and `GetRoleReferenceRules()` to resolve PolicyRules for a user from Role/ClusterRole bindings. Also contains `ConfirmNoEscalation()` for privilege escalation prevention.\n\n4. **SubjectAccessReview REST handler**: `pkg/registry/authorization/subjectaccessreview/rest.go` \u2014 `REST` struct with `Create()` that delegates to `authorizer.Authorize()` and returns `SubjectAccessReviewStatus`.\n\n5. **Bootstrap RBAC policies**: `plugin/pkg/auth/authorizer/rbac/bootstrappolicy/policy.go` (ClusterRoles, ClusterRoleBindings, NodeRules), `controller_policy.go` (ControllerRoles/ControllerRoleBindings), `namespace_policy.go` (NamespaceRoles/NamespaceRoleBindings).\n\n6. **Policy-based storage with escalation prevention**: Four policybased storage implementations that wrap StandardStorage with escalation checks:\n   - `pkg/registry/rbac/role/policybased/storage.go`\n   - `pkg/registry/rbac/clusterrole/policybased/storage.go`\n   - `pkg/registry/rbac/rolebinding/policybased/storage.go`\n   - `pkg/registry/rbac/clusterrolebinding/policybased/storage.go`\n   All use `EscalationAllowed()`, `RoleEscalationAuthorized()`, `BindingAuthorized()` from `pkg/registry/rbac/escalation_check.go` and `ConfirmNoEscalation()`/`ConfirmNoEscalationInternal()` from the validation package.",
